rc=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"窮三代，唔番工可以點<br />\n吉sir係咪財自唔洗番工?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">我喺屠場偷走咗出嚟<br />\n唔好話畀我主人知</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"有啲似白老虎既concept"}]}